      "text": "[https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCMvLz25LlhnFY5PJG0uWmeAESjdBehAoLT1gYn45rp7Hlaw=s96-c#.png]",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781366893,
      "updated": 1781366893
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9a6a0000000000ec97c6",
      "text": "himitsu",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373513,
      "updated": 1781373526
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d8ca00000000000217df8",
      "text": "2026-06-14登録",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781369983,
      "updated": 1781373882
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9b1a00000000009a2dca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373690,
      "updated": 1781373690
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9b1b00000000009a2dcb",
      "text": "こんにちは。himitsuです。",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373690,
      "updated": 1781385103
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9b8e0000000000d5a2ed",
      "text": "何書けばいいんだろう。",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373806,
      "updated": 1781385117
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9bb10000000000d5a2ef",
      "text": "頑張ります。",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373841,
      "updated": 1781373911
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9b8f0000000000d5a2ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373806,
      "updated": 1781373806
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d99120000000000ec97b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373170,
      "updated": 1781373170
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d99230000000000ec97bd",
      "text": " プロフィール",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373186,
      "updated": 1781373683
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d99120000000000ec97ba",
      "text": "  記憶力が弱い",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373170,
      "updated": 1781373395
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d99f40000000000ec97c0",
      "text": "  PCがない",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373395,
      "updated": 1781373754
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9e640000000000d5a2f4",
      "text": "  顕性遺伝を優勢遺伝と呼んでいたがドッジボール世代ではないくらいの年齢",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781374534,
      "updated": 1781374944
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2dd3f9000000000084125d",
      "text": "   [シンキングゾンビ - 北野棃也 | 少年ジャンプ＋   https://shonenjumpplus.com/episode/9253191254047171904] p.15 ドッジボール世代",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781388249,
      "updated": 1781388332
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2dc74b000000000048e811",
      "text": "  基本的に無料の範囲で生きてるので漫画とかアニメくらいしか教養がない",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781385003,
      "updated": 1781385065
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2da1ba0000000000d5a2fa",
      "text": "  2026-06-14、まだ使い方がわかってない、ぜんぜん。",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781375385,
      "updated": 1781391984
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9e850000000000d5a2f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781374565,
      "updated": 1781374566
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9a520000000000ec97c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373490,
      "updated": 1781373490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2dcbc500000000009585d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781386149,
      "updated": 1781386149
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9a520000000000ec97c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781373490,
      "updated": 1781373490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d9a530000000000ec97c3",
